text: Helmut Morbitzer (born 25 September 1955) is an Austrian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Austria Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Kirchdorf an der Krems District
